body:
The following is missed by the race detector 

```
var (
	a = "hi"
	c = make(chan struct{})
)

func f() {
	a = "bye"
	close(c)
}

func main() {
	go f()
	fmt.Println(a)
	// fmt.Printf(a)
	<-c
}
```

But changing the fmt call to `fmt.Printf` where the `a` value is copied into the format string triggers a race
